{
  "title": "Project-XS XPlus HLS Example",
  "subtitle": "基于 Project-XPlus 的 5 个 HLS kernel，以 XO 自动解析接口，JSON 注释补充 host orchestration、component 草图与 XS 模拟器映射。",
  "source_note": "规则：能从 xo 提取的接口/arg/kernel 元数据由脚本自动解析；执行顺序、依赖、host 控制、component 拆分、XS 映射等全部来自本 JSON。",
  "cfg": "connectivity_u55c.cfg",
  "artifacts": {
    "auto_discover": false,
    "csynth_dir": "vivado-log/csynth",
    "schedule_dir": "vivado-log/sched",
    "link_timing_report": "vivado-log/link/impl_1_hw_bb_locked_timing_summary_routed.rpt"
  },
  "output": {
    "json": "reports/xo_report.json",
    "html": "reports/xo_report.html"
  },
  "sequence": [
    "spmv_csr_kernel",
    "init_pcg_kernel",
    "dot_kernel",
    "update_xrz_kernel",
    "update_p_kernel"
  ],
  "sequence_descriptions": {
    "spmv_csr_kernel": "ax = A * x0 / ap = A * p",
    "init_pcg_kernel": "r / z / p / rz / rr",
    "dot_kernel": "pAp = p^T ap",
    "update_xrz_kernel": "x / r / z / rz_new / rr",
    "update_p_kernel": "p = z + beta p"
  },
  "dependencies": [
    {
      "upstream": "spmv_csr_kernel",
      "downstream": "init_pcg_kernel",
      "description": "初始化路径：ax 作为 init 的输入"
    },
    {
      "upstream": "spmv_csr_kernel",
      "downstream": "dot_kernel",
      "description": "主循环路径：ap 作为 dot 的输入"
    },
    {
      "upstream": "dot_kernel",
      "downstream": "update_xrz_kernel",
      "description": "host 读取 pAp 与 rz 后计算 alpha，并将其作为标量参数驱动 update_xrz"
    },
    {
      "upstream": "update_xrz_kernel",
      "downstream": "update_p_kernel",
      "description": "host 读取 rz_new / rz_old 后计算 beta，并将其作为标量参数驱动 update_p"
    },
    {
      "upstream": "update_p_kernel",
      "downstream": "spmv_csr_kernel",
      "description": "更新后的 p 进入下一轮 SpMV"
    }
  ],
  "host_nodes": [
    {
      "name": "host_alpha_controller",
      "role": "读取 pAp 与 rz，计算 alpha",
      "reads": ["dot_out(pAp)", "rz_old"],
      "writes": ["alpha"],
      "drives": ["update_xrz_kernel"],
      "sim_mapping": ["Kernel scheduler state", "RegPort alpha_reg", "AxiLiteIf(alpha arg)"]
    },
    {
      "name": "host_beta_controller",
      "role": "读取 rz_new / rz_old，计算 beta",
      "reads": ["metrics(rz_new)", "rz_old"],
      "writes": ["beta"],
      "drives": ["update_p_kernel"],
      "sim_mapping": ["Kernel scheduler state", "RegPort beta_reg", "AxiLiteIf(beta arg)"]
    },
    {
      "name": "host_convergence_controller",
      "role": "读取 rr，判断 break / continue",
      "reads": ["metrics(rr)", "tau", "max_iters"],
      "writes": ["loop_continue"],
      "drives": ["spmv_csr_kernel(next iter)"],
      "sim_mapping": ["CycleSimulator top loop", "RegPort rr_reg", "termination flag"]
    }
  ],
  "kernels": [
    {
      "name": "spmv_csr_kernel",
      "xo": "xo/spmv_csr_kernel.xo",
      "role": "阶段 1 / 阶段 2：稀疏乘",
      "summary": [
        "这个顶层 kernel 对应硬件中的一次 CSR SpMV。",
        "它在初始化路径上计算 ax = A * x0，在主循环路径上计算 ap = A * p。",
        "XO 里可提取参数、端口和 control protocol；行扫描语义和缓存策略则通过这里的 JSON 注释补足。"
      ],
      "reads": ["row_ptr", "col_idx", "values", "x/p"],
      "writes": ["y(ax/ap)"],
      "xs_mapping": {
        "kernel": "Kernel",
        "memory": ["global CSR", "vector cache"],
        "ports": ["AXI read row_ptr", "AXI read col_idx", "AXI read values", "AXI read x", "AXI write y"]
      },
      "xs_sim_mapping": {
        "kernel_class": "project_xs::sim::Kernel",
        "control_if": "AxiLiteIf",
        "data_if": ["AxiMasterIf(row_ptr)", "AxiMasterIf(col_idx)", "AxiMasterIf(values)", "AxiMasterIf(x)", "AxiMasterIf(y)"],
        "state_ports": ["RegPort x_local_valid", "RegPort row_acc_valid", "WirePort row_value"]
      },
      "components": [
        {
          "name": "load_x_component",
          "role": "把输入向量搬到本地缓存",
          "reads": ["x/p"],
          "writes": ["x_local"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(x)", "RegPort x_local"]
        },
        {
          "name": "csr_row_scan_component",
          "role": "按 row_ptr / col_idx 扫描 CSR 行",
          "reads": ["row_ptr", "col_idx", "values", "x_local"],
          "writes": ["row_acc"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(row_ptr)", "AxiMasterIf(col_idx)", "AxiMasterIf(values)", "RegPort row_acc"]
        },
        {
          "name": "row_commit_component",
          "role": "把一行累加结果写回 y",
          "reads": ["row_acc"],
          "writes": ["y(ax/ap)"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(y)", "WirePort row_value"]
        }
      ],
      "component_edges": [
        {"upstream": "load_x_component", "downstream": "csr_row_scan_component", "description": "缓存向量后进入按行扫描"},
        {"upstream": "csr_row_scan_component", "downstream": "row_commit_component", "description": "每行聚合完成后提交输出"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "init_pcg_kernel",
      "xo": "xo/init_pcg_kernel.xo",
      "role": "初始化阶段",
      "summary": [
        "把 Jacobi-PCG 的前缀步骤合并在一个 kernel 内完成。",
        "包括 r = b - ax、z = M^-1 r、p = z 以及 rz / rr 的 reduction。",
        "XO 只知道它有哪些参数和端口；这里的 JSON 负责说明内部逻辑拆分。"
      ],
      "reads": ["b", "ax", "m_inv"],
      "writes": ["r", "z", "p", "metrics(rz, rr)"],
      "xs_mapping": {
        "kernel": "Kernel",
        "memory": ["rhs", "ax buffer", "jacobi inverse"],
        "ports": ["AXI read b", "AXI read ax", "AXI read m_inv", "AXI write r/z/p/metrics"]
      },
      "xs_sim_mapping": {
        "kernel_class": "project_xs::sim::Kernel",
        "control_if": "AxiLiteIf",
        "data_if": ["AxiMasterIf(b)", "AxiMasterIf(ax)", "AxiMasterIf(m_inv)", "AxiMasterIf(r/z/p/metrics)"],
        "state_ports": ["RegPort r_stage", "RegPort z_stage", "RegPort p_stage", "RegPort metrics_stage"]
      },
      "components": [
        {
          "name": "residual_component",
          "role": "计算 r = b - ax",
          "reads": ["b", "ax"],
          "writes": ["r"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(b)", "AxiMasterIf(ax)", "RegPort r_stage"]
        },
        {
          "name": "jacobi_apply_component",
          "role": "计算 z = M^-1 r",
          "reads": ["r", "m_inv"],
          "writes": ["z"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(m_inv)", "RegPort r_stage", "RegPort z_stage"]
        },
        {
          "name": "seed_direction_component",
          "role": "初始化 p = z",
          "reads": ["z"],
          "writes": ["p"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["RegPort z_stage", "RegPort p_stage"]
        },
        {
          "name": "rz_rr_reduce_component",
          "role": "归约 rz / rr 到 metrics",
          "reads": ["r", "z"],
          "writes": ["metrics(rz, rr)"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["RegPort r_stage", "RegPort z_stage", "RegPort metrics_stage"]
        }
      ],
      "component_edges": [
        {"upstream": "residual_component", "downstream": "jacobi_apply_component", "description": "r 进入 Jacobi"},
        {"upstream": "jacobi_apply_component", "downstream": "seed_direction_component", "description": "z 直接成为初始方向"},
        {"upstream": "residual_component", "downstream": "rz_rr_reduce_component", "description": "r 进入 reduction"},
        {"upstream": "jacobi_apply_component", "downstream": "rz_rr_reduce_component", "description": "z 进入 reduction"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "dot_kernel",
      "xo": "xo/dot_kernel.xo",
      "role": "标量归约阶段",
      "summary": [
        "当前主循环里只负责计算 pAp = p^T ap。",
        "XO 能给出 out[0] 是一个 addressable port 绑定的 scalar 输出。",
        "更细的归约行为、acc 寄存语义和 component 草图由 JSON 提供。"
      ],
      "reads": ["a", "b"],
      "writes": ["out[0]"],
      "xs_mapping": {
        "kernel": "KernelComponent or reduction Kernel",
        "memory": ["vector a", "vector b"],
        "ports": ["AXI read a", "AXI read b", "AXI write out"]
      },
      "xs_sim_mapping": {
        "kernel_class": "project_xs::sim::Kernel or KernelComponent",
        "control_if": "AxiLiteIf",
        "data_if": ["AxiMasterIf(a)", "AxiMasterIf(b)", "AxiMasterIf(out)"],
        "state_ports": ["RegPort dot_acc", "WirePort dot_out"]
      },
      "components": [
        {
          "name": "dot_mulacc_component",
          "role": "逐元素乘加累积",
          "reads": ["a", "b"],
          "writes": ["acc"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(a)", "AxiMasterIf(b)", "RegPort dot_acc"]
        },
        {
          "name": "dot_commit_component",
          "role": "把累计值写到 out[0]",
          "reads": ["acc"],
          "writes": ["out[0]"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["RegPort dot_acc", "AxiMasterIf(out)"]
        }
      ],
      "component_edges": [
        {"upstream": "dot_mulacc_component", "downstream": "dot_commit_component", "description": "累加结束后提交标量"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "update_xrz_kernel",
      "xo": "xo/update_xrz_kernel.xo",
      "role": "向量更新阶段",
      "summary": [
        "这一层把与 alpha 绑定的一轮向量更新合并到一个 kernel 中。",
        "包括 x / r / z 更新以及 rz_new / rr 的重新归约。",
        "XO 能确定 alpha 是 control scalar、其余向量是 addressable 参数；内部阶段仍靠 JSON 注释表达。"
      ],
      "reads": ["p", "r", "ap", "m_inv", "alpha"],
      "writes": ["x", "r", "z", "metrics(rz_new, rr)"],
      "xs_mapping": {
        "kernel": "Kernel",
        "memory": ["state vectors", "ap buffer", "jacobi inverse"],
        "ports": ["AXI read/write x", "AXI read p", "AXI read/write r", "AXI read ap", "AXI read m_inv", "AXI write z/metrics"]
      },
      "xs_sim_mapping": {
        "kernel_class": "project_xs::sim::Kernel",
        "control_if": "AxiLiteIf",
        "data_if": ["AxiMasterIf(x)", "AxiMasterIf(p)", "AxiMasterIf(r)", "AxiMasterIf(ap)", "AxiMasterIf(m_inv)", "AxiMasterIf(z/metrics)"],
        "state_ports": ["RegPort x_stage", "RegPort r_stage", "RegPort z_stage", "RegPort metrics_stage"]
      },
      "components": [
        {
          "name": "update_x_component",
          "role": "计算 x = x + alpha p",
          "reads": ["x", "p", "alpha"],
          "writes": ["x"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(x)", "AxiMasterIf(p)", "RegPort x_stage"]
        },
        {
          "name": "update_r_component",
          "role": "计算 r = r - alpha ap",
          "reads": ["r", "ap", "alpha"],
          "writes": ["r"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(r)", "AxiMasterIf(ap)", "RegPort r_stage"]
        },
        {
          "name": "jacobi_apply_component",
          "role": "根据新 r 计算 z = M^-1 r",
          "reads": ["r", "m_inv"],
          "writes": ["z"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["RegPort r_stage", "AxiMasterIf(m_inv)", "RegPort z_stage"]
        },
        {
          "name": "rz_rr_reduce_component",
          "role": "根据新 r / z 归约 rz_new / rr",
          "reads": ["r", "z"],
          "writes": ["metrics(rz_new, rr)"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["RegPort r_stage", "RegPort z_stage", "RegPort metrics_stage"]
        }
      ],
      "component_edges": [
        {"upstream": "update_x_component", "downstream": "update_r_component", "description": "共享 alpha，同轮更新"},
        {"upstream": "update_r_component", "downstream": "jacobi_apply_component", "description": "新 r 进入 Jacobi"},
        {"upstream": "update_r_component", "downstream": "rz_rr_reduce_component", "description": "新 r 进入 reduction"},
        {"upstream": "jacobi_apply_component", "downstream": "rz_rr_reduce_component", "description": "新 z 进入 reduction"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "update_p_kernel",
      "xo": "xo/update_p_kernel.xo",
      "role": "方向更新阶段",
      "summary": [
        "这一层只负责方向向量更新 p = z + beta p。",
        "XO 能确定 beta 是 control scalar、z/p 是 addressable 参数。",
        "在 XS 里它很适合被视为最轻量的一类 vector update 组件。"
      ],
      "reads": ["z", "p", "beta"],
      "writes": ["p"],
      "xs_mapping": {
        "kernel": "KernelComponent or vector update Kernel",
        "memory": ["z buffer", "p buffer"],
        "ports": ["AXI read z", "AXI read/write p"]
      },
      "xs_sim_mapping": {
        "kernel_class": "project_xs::sim::Kernel or KernelComponent",
        "control_if": "AxiLiteIf",
        "data_if": ["AxiMasterIf(z)", "AxiMasterIf(p)"],
        "state_ports": ["RegPort p_stage"]
      },
      "components": [
        {
          "name": "direction_update_component",
          "role": "计算 p = z + beta p",
          "reads": ["z", "p", "beta"],
          "writes": ["p"],
          "xs_mapping": "KernelComponent",
          "sim_ports": ["AxiMasterIf(z)", "AxiMasterIf(p)", "RegPort p_stage"]
        }
      ],
      "component_edges": []
    }
  ]
}
